                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-lg-6 book-slide-right">
                <div class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded p-4 p-lg-5">
                    <h2 class="h3 text-primary mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>At Literary Haven, we're committed to:</p>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> Promoting literacy and a love for reading</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> Supporting diverse authors and perspectives</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> Creating a welcoming space for our community</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> Offering personalized recommendations</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> Hosting events that bring readers together</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>We strive to be more than just a bookstoreâ€”we aim to be your literary companion on every step of your reading journey.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5 bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="container py-4">
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center book-float">
                <i class="fas fa-users fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                <h3 class="h4 mb-3">Our Team</h3>
                <p>Our passionate team of bibliophiles is always ready to help you discover your next great read.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center book-float" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                <i class="fas fa-book-reader fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                <h3 class="h4 mb-3">Book Clubs</h3>
                <p>Join our monthly book clubs where we explore different genres and engage in thoughtful discussions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center book-float" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                <h3 class="h4 mb-3">Events</h3>
                <p>From author signings to children's story hours, we host events that celebrate the joy of reading.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>